measurements.description: One hundred three flowers and 19 buds on 12 up-to 17-cm inflorescences; flowers light yellow; sepals and petals spotted brick red basally, random sepals and petals streaked brick red; lip saccate, overlaid orange on mentum, gold spot on apex, lateral lobes overlaid orange; substance firm; texture crystalline.
